XML/Generator/RSS10/ev version 0.01
=====================================

This module extends Dave Rolsky's XML::Generator::RSS10 to
support the RSS 1.0 Event module.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

This module requires:

   XML::Generator::RSS10
	DateTime
	DateTime::Format::W3CDTF
	Params::Validate


